WEBVTT

00:03:58.292 --> 00:04:01.226
and an officer from the city walks in

00:04:01.250 --> 00:04:03.559
and tells me,

00:04:03.583 --> 00:04:06.458
"Sister, what are you doing here?"

00:04:07.500 --> 00:04:10.226
I turned and looked
to see what was happening

00:04:10.250 --> 00:04:11.833
at the respite center.

00:04:12.792 --> 00:04:15.393
I was amazed at what I was seeing.

00:04:15.417 --> 00:04:18.184
There were hundreds of volunteers

00:04:18.208 --> 00:04:23.184
helping so many families there
that needed help.

00:04:23.208 --> 00:04:26.643
Giving them ways to get cleaned up

00:04:26.667 --> 00:04:30.309
and to get clean clothing, food,